<% content_for :title, "SpeakFlow | Preview Membership Checkout" %>

<main class="page">
  <section class="surface surface--preview-admin">
    <div class="container surface__inner">
      <div class="admin-preview-shell">
        <%= render "preview/student/memberships/nav" %>

        <section class="admin-preview-main">
          <section class="page-section">
            <div class="section-heading">
              <h1 class="section-title">가입 결제 테스트 페이지</h1>
              <p class="section-copy">
                월정액 가입 전 마지막으로 확인해야 할 건 가격보다도 갱신 정책, 제공 기능, 해지 가능성입니다.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="page-section">
            <div class="detail-grid preview-checkout-grid">
              <article class="surface-card admin-preview-panel">
                <span class="pill pill--accent">선택한 플랜</span>
                <div class="membership-card membership-card--featured membership-card--checkout">
                  <div class="membership-card__headline">
                    <strong><%= @selected_plan[:name] %></strong>
                    <p><%= @selected_plan[:pitch] %></p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="commerce-price commerce-price--membership">
                    <strong><%= number_to_currency(@selected_plan[:price], unit: "₩", precision: 0) %></strong>
                    <span>다음 결제 예정일 <%= @next_billing_date.strftime("%Y.%m.%d") %></span>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="admin-preview-note">
                  <strong>정책 안내</strong>
                  <p>월정액은 언제든 해지 가능하고, 해지 전까지는 강의 열람과 리허설 제출이 유지되는 구조를 가정합니다.</p>
                </div>
              </article>

              <article class="summary-panel admin-preview-panel">
                <span class="pill">결제 요약</span>
                <div class="meta-list">
                  <div class="meta-item"><span>첫 달 결제</span><strong><%= number_to_currency(@selected_plan[:price], unit: "₩", precision: 0) %></strong></div>
                  <div class="meta-item"><span>자동 갱신</span><strong>매월 동일 금액</strong></div>
                  <div class="meta-item"><span>포함 기능</span><strong><%= @selected_plan[:highlights].first %></strong></div>
                </div>
                <div class="button-row">
                  <%= link_to "가입 완료 시안 보기", preview_student_membership_account_path, class: "button button--primary button--small" %>
                </div>
              </article>
            </div>
          </section>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
